abstract: The steamer Chcrokee, Captain WINDLE, arrived at this port on Thursday, from Chagres, with the California mails which reached that place by the Golden Gate. abstract: By this arrival, we have news from the Sandwich Islands to the 10th December. There is nothing of Importance. There had not been the slightest improvement in the market, and trade continued dull.
